Trend decider - Sport | Futures – 5 min | 15 min | 1 hr | 1 Day: 

Do NOT go below 3 min for Entry, Re-Entry, TL BO, SL, use 1 min only to draw TL 

TL to be connecting using swings only, use Lux-Algo Trendline swing with lookback 3  

Reversal on Strong Bullish or Bearish day (RSI >55 and <45 in both 1 hr. & 15 min) only below conditions are satisfied both in Spot and Option chart  

5 min | 15 min – Trend line BO candle close is must 

Previous swing is too steep, then ignore TL, candle close above / below previous swing high / low  

Double Top (DT) | Double Bottom(DT) - RSI divergence is must in both 5 min | 15 min 

Trend Side  

TL break in 3 min | 5 min in Option is sufficient  

High Probability - Combine DB/DT with Trend...In downtrend try DT | In uptrend try DB 

Trend Side – DB / DT – just 5 min divergence is sufficient  

Re-Entry – Option Buy (after Trend side confirmation): 

3 min | 5 min – Bullish engulf (when no swing is there) - break above previous candle high candle (on aggressive move) close confirmation is always the best , not recommended in sideways market  

3 min | 5 min - Bullish Trend line break out (Once two swing is formed for TL) – candle close confirmation - connecting lower top swing highs   

Option - Initial stoploss & Partial booking targets (50%)  

Initial SL - Entry Breakout (BO) candle low | Previous candle of Entry BO candle low 

Initial Targets - 5 min Option chart – Book 50% at Initial Target say 50EMA, VWAP(Century), VWAP 200 EMA using Limit Order, reversal trade initial target 50 EMA, if above 50 EMA then target 200 EMA 

Remaining position keep trailing stoploss or entry price (not to get into loss)  

Option – Trailing stoploss (50%)  for ultimate Targets 

On non-aggressive move 5 min | 3 min chart - Swing lows  

On Aggressive Wave C move -  Previous 5 min | 3 min - Solid Candle low / Red Candle low followed by Green Candles / Red candle close below 5 EMA in 5 min | 3 min 

Keep Trailing Stoploss if you are not able to view the market (may be meeting or sleeping)  

Option - Ultimate Targets: 

15 min Option chart - Ultimate Target - Trend line | Resistance Zone, also keep watch for Wave C 

Spot | Future - Trend Line & Swing - Resistance & Support in 15 min | 1 hour chart  

 

